  "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
  "body": "In Helm v2 the Capabilities included `TillerVersion` which would allow you to target and work with different minor versions of Helm. When Tiller went away so did the ability to detect the minor version of Helm.\r\n\r\nThe idea is to add this back as `HelmVersion` and available though Capabilities.\r\n\r\nNote, I'm filing this but not expecting to add this until after v3.0.0 is released.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
